Get started - do a little mapping, or even just get a taste for making spatial data
Graduate to JOSM - get the basic desktop software and work faster
Feed the map - do some stuff with mobile phone apps that you or others can later use to map
Maps in your pocket - see some mobile apps that use the openstreetmap api                        
Download - take this data and make something                       
Wiki it - add some more detail to the wiki pages
Bloggo - suggest a blog article in English, Sesotho or Esperanza
Socialise - say hi on whatsapp, twitter, Facebook, slack, or reddit
